2007-04-18  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan <thep@linux.thai.net>

	* nectec/Loma.sfd:
	  - Simplify splines for all glyphs.
	  - Use glyph references where possible, including Sara Am's
	    components and combining marks' PUA variations.

