2006-03-26  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan <thep@linux.thai.net>

	* tlwg/{Purisa,TlwgMono,TlwgTypewriter}*.sfd:  Removed XUID field.
	The XUID for TlwgTypewriter-Bold[Oblique].sfd were incomplete and
	caused error with dvips. And, according to Fontforge doc, this field
	and UniqueID were said by Adobe to be unnecessary.

