2005-01-31  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan <thep@linux.thai.net>

	* scripts/Makefile.am, +scripts/{eng,thai}kernpairs.txt:
	Add kern pairs lists, for use in auto kerning. Engish kern pairs
	were taken from FontForge documentation, which were in turn taken
	from Adobe list. Some pairs were commented out, based on experiment.
	Thai kern pairs were listed from experiment.

2005-01-30  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan <thep@linux.thai.net>

	* nf/Kinnari*.sfd:
	More spline clean-ups (mostly duplicated spline removals).
	
	* nf/Kinnari-[Bold]Italic.sfd:
