	Add GPOS, GSUB.

2004-07-29  Theppitak Karoonboonyanan <thep@linux.thai.net>

	* tlwg/Purisa.sfd:
	Scale up 126% (based on relative average X-height with Comic Sans).
	No BlueValues nor hint to adjust for this font.

