	* db/DBThaiText*.sfd:
	Scale up 145% (based on relative X-height with Arial).
	Adjust BlueValues accordingly.

	* nf/Kinnari*.sfd:
	Scale up 153.6% (based on relative X-height with Times New Roman).
	Adjust BlueValues accordingly.

